column2: Boat Rides at Center for Wooden Boats
column5:
Sundays; generally depart between 11am and 3pm. Rides are 45 min-1 hr long.  Year-round, rain or shine.  Sign up in-person starting at 10am every Sunday (open all day); first-come, first-served. 200 spots available for a given day.  Can walk around after signing up; arrive 20 min prior to time slot.  1 person may sign up for 3 additional people (so total of 4).  Arrive early especially on sunny days/holidays to guarantee a spot.
Walking the docks, exploring the boats and browsing the exhibits is always free of charge.
1st Saturday each month 10-11:30am.  Free tour of historic Paramount Theatre.
